  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 161.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I've been a part time soldier or full time soldier and almost all my life-- --and racked up a total of over 15 years of what was called active duty.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Since I retired from both the military in '77 and civilian job in '79m my wife and I decided that we were pretty well off financially and we decided we'd see the world.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we have traveled extensively throughout Europe and the Pacific since I retired until a little over three years ago, we got the worst shock of our lives.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Our 16-- one of our grad 16-year-old grandson, who was a twin, twin boys, was killed in a drive-by shooting by some kid that he didn't even know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He wasn't the intended target, but he's the one who died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, the kid that killed him was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at that time, we had no law whatsoever regarding juveniles and handguns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A kid 10 years old could pack a gun around, and they were doing it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were having-- in the particular summer that my grandson was killed, there were something like 20 juveniles who were killed by handguns.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I helped them-- I decided I wasn't going to sit around and grieve about my grandson-- --that I would do something about it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I got together with some influential people here in Colorado-- the district attorney's office in Denver and some others-- and we formed an organization called PUNCH, Parents United No Children's Handguns.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we met with the governor and he agreed to call a special session of the legislature that year to consider making it a crime for juveniles under the age of 18 to be carrying handguns.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
